snippet.title: Narcissistic traits I heard from Amber Heard speaking to Johnny Depp: #justiceforjohnny
snippet.description:
This is an example of how people can use the judicial system to hurt a victim and try and gain facade management. Control by threats, smearing, gaslighting, blame-shifting, deflection, projection, triangulation, word salad, flying monkeys. It has it all. My opinion is this is an emotionally abusive relationship and Johnny Depp is Trauma bonded. My opinion of conversations I heard. 

npd #justiceforjohnnydepp #justiceforjohnny #narcissist
